# AllCases

**Associated Type**

A type that can represent a collection of all values of this type.

## Declaration

```swift
associatedtype AllCases : Collection = [Self] where Self == Self.AllCases.Element
```

## Accessing Cases

- **allCases**: A collection of all values of this type.
